message:
[Game] WorldId for Housing fix (#403)

- Changed DefaultWorldId to 0 (again)
- Building a new world no longer overrides the world and instance Id
- Removed WorldId's from the default character templates so they will always fall-back to whatever the main_world is.

deleted: house.Transform = new Transform(house, null, 1, zoneId, 1, posX, posY, posZ, zRot);
